"<replaceable>range</replaceable> and returns the matched range. Search is "
"performed backwards if the optional boolean parameter "
"<replaceable>backwards</replaceable> is set to <literal>true</literal>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Sets the cursor position to <replaceable>line</replaceable> and "
#| "<replaceable>column</replaceable>."
msgid ""
"The returned range is invalid (see Range.isValid()) if <replaceable>pattern</"
"replaceable> is not found in <replaceable>range</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Règle la position du curseur à <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> et "
"<replaceable>colonne</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3237
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Since: &kde; 5.0"
msgid "Since: &kde-frameworks; 5.97"
msgstr "Depuis: &kde; 5.0"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Document API"
msgstr "L'API du document"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever a script is being executed, there is a global variable "
"<quote><literal>document</literal></quote> representing the current active "
"document. The following is a list of all available Document functions."
msgstr ""
"Dès l'instant où un script est exécuté, il existe une variable globale "
"<quote><literal>document</literal></quote> représentant le dossier actif "
"actuel. Voici une liste des fonctions Document disponibles."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.fileName();"
msgstr "String document.fileName();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the document's filename or an empty string for unsaved text buffers."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le nom de fichier du document ou une chaine vide pour les tampons "
"de texte non enregistrés."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3263
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.url();"
msgstr "String document.url();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3264
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Returns the document's full url or an empty string for unsaved text "
#| "buffers."
msgid ""
"Returns the document's full &URL; or an empty string for unsaved text "
"buffers."
msgstr ""
"Retourne l'URL complet du document ou une chaîne vide pour les tampons de "
"texte non enregistrés."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.mimeType();"
msgstr "String document.mimeType();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3272
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Returns the document's mime type or the mime type <literal>application/"
#| "octet-stream</literal> if no appropriate mime type could be found."
msgid ""
"Returns the document's &MIME; type or the &MIME; type <literal>application/"
"octet-stream</literal> if no appropriate &MIME; type could be found."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le type MIME du document ou le type MIME <literal>application/octet-"
"stream</literal> s'il est impossible de trouver un type MIME approprié."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3280
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.encoding();"
msgstr "String document.encoding();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the currently used encoding to save the file."
msgstr "Retourne l'encodage actuellement utilisé pour enregistrer le fichier."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3287
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.highlightingMode();"
msgstr "String document.highlightingMode();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the global highlighting mode used for the whole document."
msgstr "Retourne la coloration générale utilisée pour tout le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.highlightingModeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.highlightingModeAt(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>pos</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the highlighting mode used at the given position in the document."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la coloration utilisée à la position donnée indiquée par le curseur "
"dans le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Array document.embeddedHighlightingModes();"
msgstr "Array document.embeddedHighlightingModes();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns an array of highlighting modes embedded in this document."
msgstr "Retourne une liste des colorations utilisées dans le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.isModified();"
msgstr "bool document.isModified();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the document has unsaved changes "
"(modified), otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le document contient des changements "
"non enregistrés (modifiés), sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid "String document.text();"
msgstr "String document.text();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the entire content of the document in a single text string. Newlines "
"are marked with the newline character <quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le contenu entier du document en une seule chaine de texte. Les "
"nouvelles lignes sont marquées avec le caractère de saut de ligne "
"<quote><literal>\\n</literal></quote>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.text(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Début</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne-Depuis</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Vers</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne-Vers</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>depuis</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Curseur<replaceable>vers</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.text(<parameter>Range <replaceable>intervalle</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the text in the given range. It is recommended to use the cursor and "
"range based version for better readability of the source code."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le texte dans l'intervalle donné. Il est recommandé d'utiliser la "
"version correspondant au curseur et à l'intervalle pour avoir une meilleure "
"lisibilité du code source."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.line(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.line(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the given text line as string. The string is empty if the requested "
"line is out of range."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la ligne de texte donnée sous la forme d'une chaine. La chaine est "
"vide si la ligne demandée est en dehors de l'intervalle."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.wordAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the word at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Retourne le mot à la position donnée du curseur."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Range document.wordRangeAt(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Return the range of the word at the given cursor position. The returned "
"range is invalid (see Range.isValid()), if the text position is after the "
"end of a line. If there is no word at the given cursor, an empty range is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Retourne l'intervalle du mot à la position indiquée par le curseur. Cet "
"intervalle est invalide (voir Range.isValid()) si la position du texte se "
"trouve après la fin de la ligne. Retourne un intervalle vide s'il n'y a "
"aucun mot à l'endroit où se trouve le curseur. "

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.charAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.charAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.charAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"String document.charAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the character at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Retourne le caractère la position donnée du curseur."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.firstChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.firstChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"that is not a whitespace. The first character is at column 0. If the line is "
"empty or only contains whitespace characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le premier caractère dans la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> "
"donnée, qui n'est pas un caractère d'espacement. Le premier caractère se "
"trouve à la colonne 0. Si la ligne est vide ou ne contient que des "
"caractères d'espacement, la chaine retournée est vide."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.lastChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.lastChar(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last character in the given <replaceable>line</replaceable> that "
"is not a whitespace. If the line is empty or only contains whitespace "
"characters, the returned string is empty."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le dernier caractère dans la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> "
"donnée, qui n'est pas un caractère d'espacement. Si la ligne est vide ou ne "
"contient que des caractères d'espacement, la chaine retournée est vide."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isSpace(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the character at the given cursor "
"position is a whitespace, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le caractère à la position donnée du "
"curseur est un caractère d'espacement, sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères <replaceable>texte</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"bool document.matchesAt(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères "
"<replaceable>texte</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable> matches at the corresponding cursor position, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le <replaceable>texte</replaceable> "
"donné concorde avec la position correspondante du curseur, sinon "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.startsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>texte</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>ignorer-Espaces</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line starts with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether leading "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si la ligne commence par "
"<replaceable>texte</replaceable>, sinon <literal>false</literal>. L'argument "
"<replaceable>ignorer-Espaces</replaceable> contrôle si les caractères "
"d'espacement de début sont ou non ignorés."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.endsWith(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>texte</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>bool <replaceable>ignorer-Espaces</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the line ends with <replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>, otherwise <literal>false</literal>. The argument "
"<replaceable>skipWhiteSpaces</replaceable> controls whether trailing "
"whitespaces are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si la ligne se termine par "
"<replaceable>texte</replaceable>, sinon <literal>false</literal>. L' "
"argument <replaceable>ignorer-Espaces</replaceable> contrôle si les "
"caractères d'espacement sont ou non ignorés."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.setText(<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.setText(<parameter>String <replaceable>texte</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the entire document text."
msgstr "Définit le texte entier du document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid "bool document.clear();"
msgstr "bool document.clear();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the entire text in the document."
msgstr "Supprime le texte entier dans le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.truncate(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Truncate the given line at the given column or cursor position. Returns "
"<literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal> if the given "
"line is not part of the document range."
msgstr ""
"Tronque la ligne donnée à la colonne ou la position de curseur donnée. "
"Retourne <literal>true</literal> en cas de succès ou <literal>false</"
"literal>, si la ligne donnée ne fait pas partie de l'intervalle de document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères <replaceable>texte</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères "
"<replaceable>texte</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the <replaceable>text</replaceable> at the given cursor position. "
"Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal>, if "
"the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Insère le <replaceable>texte</replaceable> à la position donnée du curseur. "
"Retourne <literal>true</literal> en cas de succès ou <literal>false</"
"literal>, si le document est en mode lecture seule."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Depuis</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne-Depuis</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Vers</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne-Vers</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>depuis</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Curseur <replaceable>vers</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>intervalle</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the text in the given range. Returns <literal>true</literal> on "
"success, or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Supprime le texte dans l'intervalle donné. Retourne <literal>true</literal> "
"en cas de succès ou <literal>false</literal>, si le document est en mode "
"lecture seule."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>texte</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts text in the given line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, "
"or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the "
"line is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Insère du texte dans la ligne donnée. Retourne <literal>true</literal> en "
"cas de succès ou <literal>false</literal>, si le document est en mode "
"lecture seule ou si la ligne n'est pas dans l'intervalle du document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the given text line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or "
"<literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the line "
"is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Supprime la ligne de texte donnée. Retourne <literal>true</literal> en cas "
"de succès ou <literal>false</literal>, si le document est en mode lecture "
"seule ou si la ligne n'est pas dans l'intervalle du document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wraps the line at the given cursor position. Returns <literal>true</literal> "
"on success, otherwise <literal>false</literal>, &eg; if line &lt; 0."
msgstr ""
"Tronque la ligne à la position indiquée par le curseur. Retourne "
"<literal>true</literal> en cas de succès, sinon <literal>false</literal>. "
"Par exemple si la ligne &lt; 0."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Début</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>ligne-Fin</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the lines from <replaceable>startLine</replaceable> to "
"<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>. Two succeeding text lines are always "
"separated with a single space."
msgstr ""
"Joint les lignes de <replaceable>ligne-Début</replaceable> à "
"<replaceable>ligne-Fin</replaceable>. Deux lignes de texte consécutives sont "
"toujours séparées par un seul espace."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.lines();"
msgstr "int document.lines();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of lines in the document."
msgstr "Retourne le nombre de lignes dans le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>True</literal>, si la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> "
"contient actuellement des données non enregistrées."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3527 development.docbook:3539 development.docbook:3550
#: development.docbook:3562 development.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 5.0"
msgstr "Depuis: &kde; 5.0"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> was "
"changed, but the document was saved. Hence, the line currently does not "
"contain any unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>True</literal>, si la<replaceable>ligne</replaceable> a "
"été modifiée, mais que le document a été enregistré. Par conséquent, la "
"ligne ne contient actuellement aucune donnée non enregistrée."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data or was changed before."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>True</literal>, si la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> "
"contient actuellement des données non enregistrées ou si elle a été modifiée "
"auparavant."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>down</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>début-de-Ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>down</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the next touched line starting at <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. The search is performed either upwards or downwards depending "
"on the search direction specified in <replaceable>down</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Recherche la TouchedLine à partir de la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable>. La "
"recherche est effectuée vers le haut ou vers le bas du document selon "
"l'information spécifiée dans <replaceable>down</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.length();"
msgstr "int document.length();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of characters in the document."
msgstr "Retourne le nombre de caractères dans le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the <replaceable>line</replaceable>'s length."
msgstr "Retourna la longueur de la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editBegin();"
msgstr "void document.editBegin();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts an edit group for undo/redo grouping. Make sure to always call "
"<function>editEnd()</function> as often as you call <function>editBegin()</"
"function>. Calling <function>editBegin()</function> internally uses a "
"reference counter, &ie;, this call can be nested."
msgstr ""
"Démarre un groupe d'édition pour regrouper les opérations Annuler / Refaire. "
"Veillez à toujours appeler <function>editEnd()</function> aussi souvent que "
"vous appelez <function>editBegin()</function>. L'appel de "
"<function>editBegin()</function> utilise un compteur de référence en "
"interne, c'est-à-dire que cet appel peut être imbriqué."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3596
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editEnd();"
msgstr "void document.editEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ends an edit group. The last call of <function>editEnd()</function> (&ie; "
"the one for the first call of <function>editBegin()</function>) finishes the "
"edit step."
msgstr ""
"Termine un groupe d'édition. Le dernier appel de <function>editEnd()</"
"function> (c'est-à-dire celui qui fait le pendant avec le premier appel de "
"<function>editBegin()</function>) met fin à l'étape d'édition."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la première colonne, contenant des caractères autres que des "
"caractères d'espacement, dans la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> donnée. "
"S'il n'y a que des caractères d'espacement dans la ligne, la valeur de "
"retour est <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la dernière colonne, contenant des caractères autres que des "
"caractères d'espacement, dans la <replaceable>ligne</replaceable> donnée. "
"S'il n'y a que des caractères d'espacement dans la ligne, la valeur de "
"retour est <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la colonne contenant des caractères autres que des caractères "
"d'espacement, en commençant à la position donnée du curseur et en effectuant "
"une recherche arrière."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la colonne contenant des caractères autres que des caractères "
"d'espacement, en commençant à la position actuelle du curseur et en "
"effectuant une recherche avant."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la prochaine ligne non vide, contenant des caractères autres que "
"des caractères d'espacement, en effectuant une recherche arrière."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la prochaine ligne non vide, contenant des caractères autres que "
"des caractères d'espacement, en effectuant une recherche avant."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>caractère</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> can be part "
"of a word, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le <replaceable>caractère</replaceable> "
"donné contenant l'<replaceable>attribut</replaceable> donné peuvent faire "
"partie d'un mot, sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>caractère</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> is suited "
"to wrap a line, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le <replaceable>caractère</replaceable> "
"donné contenant l'<replaceable>attribut</replaceable> donné est approprié "
"pour encapsuler une ligne, sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>startAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribut-Début</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribut-Fin</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if a range starting and ending with the "
"given attributes is suited to be commented out, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si un intervalle commençant et se "
"terminant par les attributs données est approprié pour être mis en "
"commentaire, sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for single line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne l'indicateur de commentaires pour les commentaires à une seule "
"ligne pour un <replaceable>attribut</replaceable> donné."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the start of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne l'indicateur de commentaires pour le début des commentaires "
"multilignes pour un <replaceable>attribut</replaceable> donné."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the end of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne l'indicateur de commentaires pour la fin des commentaires "
"multilignes pour un <replaceable>attribut</replaceable> donné."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range document.documentRange();"
msgstr "Range document.documentRange();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a range that encompasses the whole document."
msgstr "Retourne l'intervalle qui inclut tout le document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor documentEnd();"
msgstr "Cursor documentEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns a cursor positioned at the last column of the last line in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le curseur positionné à la dernière colonne de la dernière ligne du "
"document."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Curseur <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given cursor position is positioned "
"at a valid text position. A text position is valid only if it locate at the "
"start, in the middle, or the end of a valid line. Further, a text position "
"is invalid if it is located in a Unicode surrogate."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal> si la position indiquée par le curseur se "
"trouve être sur une position de texte valable. Une position de texte est "
"valable uniquement si elle se trouve au début, au milieu ou à la fin d'une "
"ligne valable. De plus, une position de texte n'est pas valable si elle se "
"trouve sur un caractère de remplacement Unicode."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the attribute at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Retourne l'attribut à la position donnée du curseur."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute at the given cursor "
"position equals <replaceable>attribute</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si l'attribut à la position donnée du "
"curseur est égal à <replaceable>attribut</replaceable>, sinon "
"<literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"String document.attributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the attribute name as human readable text. This is equal to the "
"<literal>itemData</literal> name in the syntax highlighting files."
msgstr ""
"Retourne le nom de l'attribut sous la forme de texte lisible par "
"l'utilisateur. Il est égal au nom <literal>itemData</literal> dans le "
"fichier de coloration syntaxique."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>name</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>nom</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttributeName(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>curseur</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>nom</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the attribute name at a certain cursor "
"position matches the given <replaceable>name</replaceable>, otherwise "
"<literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne <literal>true</literal>, si le nom de l'attribut à une certaines "
"position du curseur correspond au <replaceable>nom</replaceable> donné, "
"sinon <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.variable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.variable(<parameter>String <replaceable>clé</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>. If the document variable does not exist, the return value is "
"an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la valeur de la variable de document demandée <replaceable>clé</"
"replaceable>. Si la variable de document n'existe pas, la valeur de retour "
"est une chaine vide."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.setVariable(<parameter>String <replaceable>key</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>value</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.setVariable(<parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères <replaceable>clé</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Chaîne-de-caractères "
"<replaceable>valeur</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the value of the requested document variable <replaceable>key</"
"replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la valeur de la variable <replaceable>clé</replaceable> demandée."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also: <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Kate document variables</link>"
msgstr ""
"Voir également : <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Variable d'un document "
"Kate</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3794
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 4.8"
msgstr "Depuis: &kde; 4.8"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the first non-whitespace character in the "
"given line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la colonne virtuelle du premier caractère autre qu'un caractère "
"d'espacement dans la ligne donnée ou <literal>-1</literal>, si la ligne est "
"vide ou ne contient que des caractères d'espacement."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the virtual column of the last non-whitespace character in the given "
"line or <literal>-1</literal>, if the line is empty or contains only "
"whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"Retourne la colonne virtuelle du dernier caractère autre qu'un caractère "
"d'espacement dans la ligne donnée ou <literal>-1</literal>, si la ligne est "
"vide ou ne contient que des caractères d'espacement."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"Cursor document.toVirtualCursor(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.toVirtualColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>ligne</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>colonne</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
