#~| "Code folding allows you to hide parts of a document in the editor, "
#~| "making it easier to overview large documents. In &kate; the foldable "
#~| "regions are calculated using rules defined in the syntax highlight "
#~| "definitions, and therefore it is only available in some formats - "
